WEBVTT

00:14.140 --> 00:14.750
Yuanji.

00:17.830 --> 00:18.760
You're here too.

00:19.830 --> 00:22.000
I have something
to report to His Highness.

00:22.000 --> 00:23.800
Wuyi is injured from the caning.

00:23.920 --> 00:25.580
Lady Xie is taking care of him.

00:26.120 --> 00:29.120
Is it about Cui Jun kidnapping Lady Xie?

00:29.510 --> 00:32.170
Yes. I need to ask
His Highness for forgiveness.

00:32.200 --> 00:33.920
I let Cui Jun go.

00:35.000 --> 00:38.200
Even though the Empress Dowager
threatened me with my family,

00:38.200 --> 00:39.430
I was wrong.

00:39.920 --> 00:42.070
Jiayu was also taken away
by Cui Jun because of me

00:42.070 --> 00:43.470
and almost got into trouble.

00:43.470 --> 00:44.560
Wuyi already knew

00:45.060 --> 00:46.710
that you took Qing Long's key.

00:46.710 --> 00:47.470
What?

00:48.070 --> 00:49.730
The incident at Lingfeng Fort

00:49.960 --> 00:51.520
can no longer be kept a secret.

00:51.520 --> 00:54.640
The Phoenix Heart Tokens and the mine
have caught the noble families' attention.

00:54.640 --> 00:56.430
They will definitely make a move.

00:56.430 --> 00:58.670
The noble families have always
wanted to sabotage the reform.

00:58.670 --> 00:59.840
As soon as they find an opportunity,

00:59.840 --> 01:01.240
they won't easily let go.

01:01.670 --> 01:03.000
Wuyi had a premonition.

01:03.430 --> 01:05.560
Since the Empress Dowager
has entered the game,

01:05.560 --> 01:07.620
she won't be able to escape so easily.

01:07.920 --> 01:08.789
His Highness

01:09.710 --> 01:12.570
is going to make a move
against the Empress Dowager?

01:12.760 --> 01:15.270
In that case, I should go find him.

02:41.510 --> 02:45.430
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:45.579 --> 02:48.380
[Episode 20]

02:48.460 --> 02:50.610
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

02:58.430 --> 02:59.960
What are you zoning out for?

03:02.680 --> 03:04.800
Back then, to protect your child,

03:05.030 --> 03:06.830
you broke ties with your family.

03:07.120 --> 03:08.150
How did it feel?

03:08.910 --> 03:09.960
I was relieved.

03:10.520 --> 03:11.750
They wanted me to be buried alive
with the dead.

03:11.750 --> 03:12.880
What else could I do?

03:15.240 --> 03:17.190
I wish I could be as decisive as you.

03:18.680 --> 03:21.400
My father, brother,
and mother don't care about me,

03:21.400 --> 03:23.260
willing to sacrifice my marriage

03:23.310 --> 03:25.150
to surrender to the Empress Dowager.

03:25.150 --> 03:28.079
But I can't just abandon them.

03:29.310 --> 03:30.310
For so many years,

03:30.360 --> 03:32.560
I've hidden in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

03:32.560 --> 03:33.590
reading and studying,

03:33.590 --> 03:34.920
pretending to be sober,

03:36.310 --> 03:37.910
but actually just escaping.

03:38.310 --> 03:40.910
His Highness gave me
the divorce paper long ago,

03:40.910 --> 03:41.590
but I

03:42.800 --> 03:44.030
dare not leave.

03:44.310 --> 03:47.150
I followed my grandfather
to practice medicine from childhood

03:47.150 --> 03:48.950
and found an interesting thing.

03:49.150 --> 03:50.470
In practicing medicine,

03:50.470 --> 03:51.470
it's often the poor

03:51.470 --> 03:53.560
who are more willing to try harsh medicine
with a massive dosage.

03:53.560 --> 03:54.560
One dose down

03:54.630 --> 03:56.310
often leads to miraculous effects.

03:56.310 --> 03:58.470
However, when people
from noble families get sick,

03:58.470 --> 03:59.750
they are always
careful with their medicine,

03:59.750 --> 04:01.150
afraid of making mistakes,

04:01.150 --> 04:03.120
which turns minor illnesses
into major ones.

04:03.120 --> 04:04.000
Guess why?

04:04.150 --> 04:06.840
Maybe because those who have less

04:07.120 --> 04:08.850
are more willing to take risks.

04:10.280 --> 04:12.520
However, those who grew up in luxury

04:13.080 --> 04:14.520
are indebted to their families

04:14.520 --> 04:15.850
and controlled by them,

04:16.070 --> 04:19.160
having their wings broken
from the bottom of their hearts

04:19.160 --> 04:20.560
and having too many scruples.

04:20.560 --> 04:23.360
So it's normal that you
can't let go of your family.

04:23.750 --> 04:25.350
Everyone is born different;

04:25.630 --> 04:27.830
there's no need to live the same way.

04:31.130 --> 04:34.140
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

04:36.190 --> 04:37.050
Your Highness.

04:37.680 --> 04:38.540
Your Highness.

04:50.870 --> 04:53.240
Move. I'm going to get
the imperial physician.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.390
Her Majesty said

04:54.390 --> 04:55.830
Prince Qi was injured

04:56.000 --> 04:56.930
and needed rest.

04:57.240 --> 04:59.360
The physician will arrive later.

04:59.920 --> 05:00.780
Her Majesty...

05:05.000 --> 05:07.000
Ruisheng, is his wound really okay?

05:08.110 --> 05:10.750
Don't worry. The wounds he suffered before

05:10.750 --> 05:12.750
were 10 or 100 times worse than this,

05:13.170 --> 05:14.100
and he survived.

05:18.560 --> 05:19.240
But you can't just think

05:19.240 --> 05:20.950
that because his previous wounds
were worse,

05:20.950 --> 05:22.750
the current one doesn't matter.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.000
Ruisheng,

05:24.190 --> 05:25.790
please think of another way.

05:26.040 --> 05:27.740
Rest assured,
I'll watch him drink his medicine,

05:27.740 --> 05:29.510
without missing every single drop.

05:29.510 --> 05:30.800
As for His Highness's medicine,

05:30.800 --> 05:32.310
coptis is indeed missing.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.680
I'll add it later.

05:37.920 --> 05:38.780
Your Highness,

05:39.159 --> 05:41.090
Chan, a maid in the Eastern Palace,

05:41.270 --> 05:42.120
who is Lady Xie's

05:42.120 --> 05:43.920
dancer friend she saved before,

05:44.800 --> 05:46.390
asked someone
to send out a bag of medicine residue.

05:46.390 --> 05:47.960
Something is wrong with Prince Qi.

05:47.960 --> 05:49.090
I'm afraid it's bad.

05:49.159 --> 05:52.070
This is the only news
from the Eastern Palace recently.

05:52.070 --> 05:53.070
How could that be?

05:53.240 --> 05:55.700
Didn't they say
the arrow wound wasn't deep?

05:56.120 --> 05:58.040
Was the arrow poisoned?

06:05.190 --> 06:06.390
I had a wound on my palm

06:06.920 --> 06:08.160
and touched the arrow that day.

06:08.160 --> 06:10.620
If it were poisoned,
I would not be unharmed.

06:10.690 --> 06:12.290
Check the medicine residue.

06:15.160 --> 06:16.290
Something's wrong?

06:16.800 --> 06:17.830
I remember now.

06:18.630 --> 06:20.360
When I used to practice medicine
with my grandfather,

06:20.360 --> 06:21.480
while gathering herbs in the mountains,

06:21.480 --> 06:23.360
I came across an herb with a lily scent.

06:23.360 --> 06:24.510
Its sprouts are poisonous.

06:24.510 --> 06:26.600
When the poison acts up,
it looks like a normal high fever.

06:26.600 --> 06:28.750
The fever continues until the person dies.

06:28.750 --> 06:30.310
If a physician doesn't know
about this poison,

06:30.310 --> 06:31.750
they won't be able to find the cause.

06:31.750 --> 06:34.080
Usually, the patient dies without a cure.

06:34.950 --> 06:36.310
Was Mao poisoned too?

06:36.430 --> 06:36.920
Will he...

06:36.920 --> 06:37.650
Don't worry.

06:37.750 --> 06:39.220
This poison's symptoms are just hidden.

06:39.220 --> 06:41.420
Its toxin can be neutralized with ease.

06:45.750 --> 06:46.560
Don't worry.

06:49.000 --> 06:50.510
I remember your grandfather

06:50.510 --> 06:52.240
used to work
at the Imperial Medical Bureau.

06:52.240 --> 06:54.750
Yes, but he retired early

06:54.830 --> 06:56.950
and took me to practice medicine
among the people.

06:56.950 --> 06:58.159
He passed away a few years later.

06:58.159 --> 06:59.220
When did he retire?

06:59.310 --> 07:01.510
About 13 years ago,

07:03.000 --> 07:05.390
not long after His Majesty
ascended the throne.

07:05.390 --> 07:07.720
High fever. Poisoning.

07:08.360 --> 07:09.830
Immediately scout the guards
of the Eastern Palace

07:09.830 --> 07:10.790
and the deployment
of the Imperial Guard again.

07:10.790 --> 07:11.310
Yes.

07:13.480 --> 07:15.280
I need you to do something for me.

07:20.920 --> 07:23.120
Ruisheng, why don't we go over the wall?

07:23.120 --> 07:24.120
I know a little lightness skill,

07:24.120 --> 07:25.780
so I can carry you both inside.

07:32.060 --> 07:33.890
[Qin]

07:32.730 --> 07:33.830
Imperial Physician Qin.

07:33.830 --> 07:34.920
The old lady said,

07:35.040 --> 07:37.240
Madam Ruisheng severed ties
with the Yu family long ago.

07:37.240 --> 07:40.440
Madam Ruisheng hasn't visited
the Yu residence tonight.

07:49.070 --> 07:49.680
Brother.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.860
I need to return to the He Mansion.

07:54.000 --> 07:54.950
I'll go with you.

08:08.630 --> 08:09.430
Is it bitter?

08:10.750 --> 08:12.210
I have pear blossom candy.

08:13.830 --> 08:15.000
I like sour food.

08:17.190 --> 08:18.390
Finish this today,

08:18.830 --> 08:21.430
and I'll make you hawthorn cakes
another day.

08:22.560 --> 08:23.120
Really?

08:31.560 --> 08:33.830
No need. Just buy some hawthorns.

08:34.200 --> 08:36.600
Making hawthorn cakes is too much trouble,

08:36.840 --> 08:38.770
and peeling them hurts your hands.

08:41.669 --> 08:42.530
Your Highness.

08:43.549 --> 08:46.240
We've tried.
The Eastern Palace is indeed sealed off.

08:46.240 --> 08:47.100
We can't get in.

08:47.210 --> 08:48.550
The Imperial Guard's
movements are abnormal.

08:48.550 --> 08:49.200
The sentry rotation
at His Majesty's bedchambers

08:49.200 --> 08:50.800
has ceased since last night.

08:52.360 --> 08:54.600
The Empress Dowager
is trying to pull the same trick on Mao.

08:54.600 --> 08:57.080
The Empress Dowager
has set this stage for so long.

08:57.080 --> 08:58.610
It's time to put an end to it.

09:03.790 --> 09:05.870
Go get my court attire.

09:06.270 --> 09:08.000
Should you wear armor under it?

09:08.320 --> 09:09.870
To deal with the Empress Dowager,

09:09.870 --> 09:10.930
I don't need armor.

09:21.240 --> 09:23.580
Your Highness, Prince Qi has been having
a fever for 2 days.

09:23.580 --> 09:25.270
No one from the Imperial Medical Bureau
has come at all.

09:25.270 --> 09:25.910
Ruisheng.

09:27.840 --> 09:29.390
Tie up all the guards who have sealed off

09:29.390 --> 09:30.420
the Eastern Palace in the past few days!

09:30.420 --> 09:31.080
-Yes.
-Yes.

09:39.450 --> 09:40.020
Eunuch.

09:42.120 --> 09:44.000
What happened?
Why are you in such a panic?

09:44.000 --> 09:44.910
Y-Your Majesty,

09:44.910 --> 09:46.550
Xiao Wuyi broke into
the Eastern Palace at night

09:46.550 --> 09:47.930
to save His Highness Prince Qi.

09:47.930 --> 09:49.960
And Imperial Physician Qin was caught.

09:49.960 --> 09:51.600
Will Imperial Physician Qin
reveal what happened—

09:51.600 --> 09:52.730
Slap your own mouth.

09:52.840 --> 09:53.600
I deserve to die.

09:53.600 --> 09:54.390
I deserve to die.

09:54.390 --> 09:55.240
I deserve to die.

09:55.240 --> 09:55.720
I deserve to die.

09:55.720 --> 09:56.390
Stop.

09:58.080 --> 09:59.720
More than 20 people
in Imperial Physician Qin's family

09:59.720 --> 10:00.790
are in my hands.

10:00.790 --> 10:01.750
Even if he dies,

10:01.870 --> 10:04.000
he won't dare to leak any information.

10:04.440 --> 10:06.120
I guessed right.

10:06.600 --> 10:07.870
We really can't let them

10:07.870 --> 10:10.200
have the day
to turn the world upside down.

10:10.480 --> 10:12.540
Since His Majesty won't listen to me,

10:13.080 --> 10:15.630
I'll make the decision for him.

10:16.790 --> 10:17.870
Pass on my decree.

10:18.080 --> 10:19.010
Muster every man

10:19.200 --> 10:20.670
of the Imperial Guard

10:20.670 --> 10:21.960
who is from the He family.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.670
Make them stop Xiao Wuyi for me.

10:23.670 --> 10:24.240
Yes.

10:32.110 --> 10:33.470
You know what to do.

10:33.840 --> 10:34.360
Yes.

10:37.510 --> 10:39.360
Today is a great day.

10:39.720 --> 10:41.920
Arrange the Sun-Moon Phoenix coiffure

10:41.960 --> 10:45.390
for me for this dynastic transition.

10:46.600 --> 10:47.030
Yes.

11:10.840 --> 11:12.840
Why hasn't His Majesty drunk it yet?

11:24.360 --> 11:26.690
Please take your medicine, Your Majesty.

11:49.200 --> 11:50.600
In this Jiankang Palace,

11:51.000 --> 11:53.060
the only one who truly treats you well

11:54.390 --> 11:55.390
is me.

11:56.000 --> 11:58.240
Do you know how much effort I put in

11:58.910 --> 12:01.440
in exchange for your current status?

12:02.200 --> 12:02.910
I

12:03.480 --> 12:05.740
always remember your kindness, Mother.

12:05.960 --> 12:07.030
In that case,

12:08.480 --> 12:11.150
promise me 3 things tonight.

12:11.840 --> 12:12.440
First,

12:13.150 --> 12:14.550
stop the Beifu Reform.

12:15.720 --> 12:16.320
Second,

12:17.320 --> 12:19.580
abolish Prince Qi's position as Regent.

12:21.030 --> 12:23.630
Third, as for the position
of Crown Prince,

12:24.610 --> 12:26.870
I've found a suitable candidate for you.

12:29.030 --> 12:30.560
The third son of Prince You.

12:31.510 --> 12:33.310
What do you think, Your Majesty?

12:33.790 --> 12:34.630
Mother,

12:37.360 --> 12:38.870
what I think tonight

12:40.080 --> 12:41.410
is no longer important.

12:50.120 --> 12:52.440
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

12:56.500 --> 12:58.000
What is the meaning of this?

12:58.000 --> 13:00.000
Qin Sheng murdered
Prince Qi and His Majesty.

13:00.000 --> 13:01.390
He was caught red-handed.

13:01.390 --> 13:03.840
There must be a mastermind behind it.

13:09.540 --> 13:11.810
Qin Sheng, who told you to do this?

13:12.440 --> 13:14.710
It was done by me alone.

13:12.690 --> 13:14.930
[Qin Sheng, Imperial Physician]

13:31.240 --> 13:32.510
-Nuo.
-Father.

13:32.720 --> 13:34.480
Father, why are you bleeding?

13:34.480 --> 13:36.320
Does it hurt, Father?

13:36.480 --> 13:38.120
Don't be afraid, Lord Qin.

13:38.390 --> 13:39.680
All your kin are present.

13:39.680 --> 13:41.140
Just tell us what you know.

13:46.630 --> 13:48.030
Just speak.

13:48.270 --> 13:49.870
I'll tell you. I'll tell you.

13:50.840 --> 13:52.640
That was the winter 13 years ago.

13:53.000 --> 13:54.800
Since coming south to Jiankang,

13:54.960 --> 13:57.670
after Wenxi and her son
passed away one after another,

13:57.670 --> 13:59.960
the late Emperor became ill from grief.

14:00.550 --> 14:02.150
When it came time
to appoint the Crown Prince,

14:02.150 --> 14:03.750
Prince Su and Prince Ning

14:03.840 --> 14:05.300
were the hope of the court.

14:07.000 --> 14:09.750
That night, it snowed heavily.

14:21.360 --> 14:23.120
Take this prescription.

14:23.240 --> 14:25.510
Mix it into the bird's nest soup
for a late-night snack

14:25.510 --> 14:27.370
and send the soup to every prince.

14:27.870 --> 14:29.530
Even your own flesh and blood,

14:29.720 --> 14:30.720
Prince Yan, too?

14:32.720 --> 14:33.850
To achieve our goal,

14:34.750 --> 14:36.550
we must be willing to sacrifice.

14:37.440 --> 14:39.390
I have my own way to protect my son.

14:40.440 --> 14:41.600
Three months later,

14:41.910 --> 14:44.270
Prince Su and Prince Ning
died one after another,

14:44.270 --> 14:45.870
with only Prince Yan left alive.

14:45.870 --> 14:47.670
But Prince Yan was also poisoned

14:48.270 --> 14:50.080
and became bedridden.

14:50.080 --> 14:51.200
Nonsense!

14:51.600 --> 14:53.150
His Majesty is my biological son.

14:53.150 --> 14:55.030
How could I be so cruel as to harm him?

14:55.030 --> 14:57.630
Qin Sheng, who put these words
into your mouth?

14:57.910 --> 15:00.320
Who asked you to frame me? Speak!

15:04.080 --> 15:04.720
Mother.

15:06.200 --> 15:08.730
I still remember that
in the bird's nest soup,

15:11.630 --> 15:13.630
there was a trace of lily scent.

15:14.340 --> 15:15.190
The poison

15:18.790 --> 15:20.320
was Dark Night Herb, right?

15:25.400 --> 15:26.800
Take them away first.

15:39.220 --> 15:40.670
When did you know?

15:41.720 --> 15:43.000
From the first day.

15:45.670 --> 15:47.400
Then why did you still drink it?

15:47.630 --> 15:49.240
Because since I was young,

15:51.870 --> 15:54.120
I had always wanted to please you

15:56.390 --> 15:58.550
and get your praise.

16:06.790 --> 16:07.630
In that case,

16:07.840 --> 16:09.840
do as I say tonight.

16:15.790 --> 16:17.080
I cling to life

16:17.960 --> 16:20.150
merely to get through each day.

16:20.630 --> 16:22.600
I am an incompetent emperor

16:23.750 --> 16:25.270
and an unfilial son.

16:25.960 --> 16:26.480
No.

16:27.440 --> 16:29.570
If you seek to contend and seize power,

16:29.600 --> 16:30.660
I can't control it,

16:31.600 --> 16:32.460
nor do I want to.

16:34.870 --> 16:36.440
But if the Ye Empire

16:37.080 --> 16:38.880
is really destroyed in my hands,

16:39.670 --> 16:42.130
I will be too shameless
to face my ancestors.

16:49.670 --> 16:50.600
Young Lord Xiao,

16:51.320 --> 16:52.480
how is Prince Qi?

16:54.150 --> 16:56.360
Your Majesty,
the poison has been neutralized.

16:56.360 --> 16:57.480
He is resting now.

17:03.600 --> 17:04.550
Xiao Wuyi,

17:04.960 --> 17:06.589
do you think digging up old cases

17:06.589 --> 17:08.010
can put me to death?

17:08.270 --> 17:09.550
I am the current Empress Dowager,

17:09.550 --> 17:11.109
His Majesty's biological mother.

17:11.109 --> 17:13.000
So what if I did something wrong?

17:13.589 --> 17:16.050
Besides, I have been waiting
for this moment tonight

17:16.050 --> 17:17.490
for a long time.

17:18.550 --> 17:19.240
He Tian!

17:20.720 --> 17:22.880
Xiao Wuyi conspired
to rebel in the palace.

17:22.880 --> 17:23.680
Take him down!

17:41.960 --> 17:42.790
Kneel.

17:43.400 --> 17:46.460
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

17:52.750 --> 17:54.210
Greetings, Your Majesty.

17:55.750 --> 17:57.210
Greetings, Your Majesty.

17:57.410 --> 17:58.130
Step back.

18:01.790 --> 18:02.830
It's you.

18:04.550 --> 18:06.240
You betrayed me.

18:09.680 --> 18:11.350
Young Lord Xiao entered the palace tonight

18:11.350 --> 18:13.280
to bring down the Empress Dowager.

18:13.440 --> 18:15.920
The He family kidnapped
Cui Jun for the Phoenix Heart Token

18:15.920 --> 18:16.790
and instructed Cui Jun

18:16.790 --> 18:19.720
to sow discord
between Young Lord Xiao and Prince Qi.

18:19.790 --> 18:21.440
After Cui Jun shot Prince Qi,

18:21.960 --> 18:23.920
the Empress Dowager
secretly poisoned Prince Qi

18:23.920 --> 18:25.440
to set up another Crown Prince.

18:25.440 --> 18:26.880
The evidence is conclusive.

18:26.880 --> 18:28.480
Then what are you doing here?

18:28.680 --> 18:30.550
Why don't you hurry
and report to the Empress Dowager?

18:30.550 --> 18:33.200
Are you going to betray us?

18:33.640 --> 18:35.880
We'll bring down
the Empress Dowager tonight,

18:35.880 --> 18:37.480
and I also stand as a witness.

18:38.030 --> 18:39.000
Young Lord Xiao has found out

18:39.000 --> 18:41.400
the truth behind His Majesty's ascension.

18:41.550 --> 18:42.950
Prince Su and Prince Ning

18:43.160 --> 18:45.000
were both poisoned by the Empress Dowager.

18:45.000 --> 18:46.400
Tonight, trouble arises from within.

18:46.400 --> 18:47.790
The He family has 2 choices.

18:47.790 --> 18:49.990
First, cut off a finger to save the hand.

18:50.070 --> 18:52.730
Second, die together
with the Empress Dowager.

18:54.440 --> 18:55.110
Everyone,

18:55.640 --> 18:57.880
do you want to live or die?

18:58.670 --> 18:59.670
What should we do?

19:00.550 --> 19:01.750
If you want to live,

19:02.680 --> 19:05.310
only I can protect the He family now.

19:05.480 --> 19:06.680
What are you going to do?

19:06.680 --> 19:08.200
Plead guilty

19:08.510 --> 19:09.830
and support the Beifu Reform.

19:09.830 --> 19:13.310
Absurd! The He family
is the top noble family in Jiangnan.

19:13.960 --> 19:15.760
How could we support the reform?

19:16.270 --> 19:18.790
Besides, the Empress Dowager
is His Majesty's mother.

19:18.790 --> 19:20.400
Even if His Majesty knows

19:20.400 --> 19:23.070
that the Empress Dowager
harmed Prince Su and Prince Ning,

19:23.070 --> 19:24.550
he might not do anything.

19:24.830 --> 19:26.360
What if the Empress Dowager

19:26.480 --> 19:28.540
also poisoned His Majesty back then?

19:28.960 --> 19:30.440
What if His Majesty is weak now

19:30.440 --> 19:31.880
because the poison
wasn't completely cleared,

19:31.880 --> 19:33.740
which leaves lingering effects?

19:34.030 --> 19:35.790
I have married into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

19:35.790 --> 19:37.520
I could have stayed out of this.

19:37.920 --> 19:40.850
However, the He family
is my maternal clan after all.

19:40.960 --> 19:43.110
So I still came tonight.

19:43.400 --> 19:45.200
Will you continue to follow
the Empress Dowager's sinking ship

19:45.200 --> 19:46.270
and drown together,

19:46.270 --> 19:47.920
or listen to me from now on

19:48.240 --> 19:49.300
and change course?

19:49.920 --> 19:52.480
At least, we can keep the He family safe.

19:53.480 --> 19:55.830
Choose for yourselves.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.430
The family seal is here.

20:19.880 --> 20:20.920
Very well.

20:24.260 --> 20:25.920
This is the list I've collected
over the years

20:25.920 --> 20:27.990
of the He family's forming factions

20:28.030 --> 20:29.310
and taking bribes.

20:29.760 --> 20:31.350
Please review it, Your Majesty.

20:31.350 --> 20:33.480
He Yuanji, are you crazy?

20:33.720 --> 20:35.920
Are you trying to destroy the He family?

20:36.240 --> 20:39.240
Aunt, I'm saving the He family.

20:39.830 --> 20:41.920
The He family can't keep making mistakes.

20:41.920 --> 20:43.120
Saving the He family?

20:44.790 --> 20:47.440
The He family moved south from Capital

20:48.070 --> 20:49.720
to help establish the capital in Jiankang.

20:49.720 --> 20:51.590
They have all made great contributions.

20:51.590 --> 20:54.590
I beg for mercy;
do not implicate the entire He family.

21:05.720 --> 21:08.240
Reform is the trend of the times,

21:09.030 --> 21:11.090
not the slaughter of noble families.

21:11.400 --> 21:13.240
If there are those who work together,

21:13.240 --> 21:14.840
they should be granted grace

21:15.030 --> 21:16.160
and set as examples.

21:18.000 --> 21:19.800
What about the Empress Dowager?

21:22.030 --> 21:24.290
The Empress Dowager is old and confused.

21:24.750 --> 21:26.550
Her seal should be confiscated,

21:27.240 --> 21:29.030
and she should be moved to another palace

21:29.030 --> 21:31.160
to spend her remaining years in peace.

21:45.750 --> 21:46.280
Granted.

21:51.200 --> 21:51.850
Granted?

21:54.960 --> 21:55.730
Granted?

21:56.620 --> 21:57.340
Guards.

21:58.300 --> 21:59.140
My son.

22:00.150 --> 22:00.950
Let go!

22:03.440 --> 22:06.510
My son, I did it all for you.

22:16.950 --> 22:18.560
When I got the family seal,

22:19.240 --> 22:20.500
my grandfather told me

22:20.690 --> 22:22.310
that for the future
of the entire He family,

22:22.310 --> 22:23.770
anyone can be sacrificed,

22:25.310 --> 22:26.710
including his daughter.

22:26.830 --> 22:27.510
Aunt.

22:28.240 --> 22:29.790
Your father and son

22:30.920 --> 22:32.520
have already given up on you.

22:35.960 --> 22:38.000
Do you think you can stay out of it?

22:52.550 --> 22:53.350
Your Majesty,

22:53.720 --> 22:54.750
I, He Yuanji,

22:55.240 --> 22:57.110
was granted a marriage
to Young Lord Xiao by the Empress Dowager.

22:57.110 --> 22:58.350
We have been married for 5 years.

22:58.350 --> 22:59.880
My virtue and conduct are flawed.

22:59.880 --> 23:01.210
I beg you, Your Majesty,

23:01.590 --> 23:03.550
to annul the marriage
between the Xiao and He families

23:03.550 --> 23:05.950
and allow me
and Young Lord Xiao to divorce.

23:06.030 --> 23:09.090
I am willing to lead
the He family to support his reform.

23:09.360 --> 23:09.960
Granted.

23:12.880 --> 23:15.440
The noble familie
are deeply rooted and intertwined.

23:15.440 --> 23:17.680
Even my throne was given to me by them.

23:18.450 --> 23:19.580
You shall do

23:21.630 --> 23:23.020
what I can't for me.

23:25.070 --> 23:27.920
Xiao Wuyi, I will issue a secret edict.

23:28.070 --> 23:29.720
If I die one day,

23:30.830 --> 23:32.790
let the Empress Dowager go with me,

23:33.400 --> 23:35.590
lest she exploit filial piety as an excuse

23:35.590 --> 23:37.030
to usurp power.

23:37.270 --> 23:38.000
Today,

23:39.550 --> 23:42.440
you covered up
the past court scandal for me

23:43.550 --> 23:45.680
and saved the royal family's dignity.

23:45.750 --> 23:48.400
I will play the villain
for you on another day.

23:52.200 --> 23:54.460
I thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

23:56.750 --> 23:57.790
Prince Qi, Li Mao.

24:00.310 --> 24:00.880
I am here.

24:01.160 --> 24:03.510
I bestow upon you the Nine Imperial Seals.

24:04.750 --> 24:06.950
In the future, when you act on my behalf,

24:07.110 --> 24:09.310
you do not need to ask for instructions.

24:10.310 --> 24:11.710
Thank you, Your Majesty.

24:11.790 --> 24:12.790
You shall preside

24:13.960 --> 24:15.720
as chief judge over the Cui Family Case.

24:15.720 --> 24:17.590
I receive the decree.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.110
I won.

24:53.070 --> 24:54.400
Congratulations, Mao,

24:55.070 --> 24:57.270
on successfully bringing down
the Empress Dowager

24:57.270 --> 24:59.330
and getting the Nine Imperial Seals.

25:04.400 --> 25:06.350
You did what Xiao Wuyi

25:08.070 --> 25:09.240
couldn't do.

25:18.720 --> 25:19.650
Are you leaving?

25:28.440 --> 25:30.640
Li Lejun no longer exists in this world.

25:30.920 --> 25:31.550
Mao,

25:34.520 --> 25:36.170
I will not become your stain.

25:36.440 --> 25:37.720
You are not my stain.

25:45.550 --> 25:47.030
You are my only family.

26:02.790 --> 26:07.000
Your Highness,
why do you think I will help you?

26:08.120 --> 26:10.550
If I tell Young Lord Xiao that

26:10.580 --> 26:11.910
Cui Jun is in the palace,

26:12.160 --> 26:14.220
how do you think things will turn out?

26:15.640 --> 26:17.240
If you really can't hide him,

26:18.000 --> 26:18.790
in the end,

26:19.230 --> 26:20.990
won't it still be your fault?

26:24.240 --> 26:25.720
Even if I am sacrificed,

26:26.030 --> 26:28.830
Her Majesty won't suffer any loss.

26:29.960 --> 26:31.420
Why would I sacrifice you?

26:31.680 --> 26:33.010
What do you want me to do?

26:33.790 --> 26:34.720
Release Cui Jun,

26:35.590 --> 26:36.920
take Xie Jiayu hostage,

26:37.360 --> 26:38.560
and have him shoot me.

26:39.790 --> 26:40.520
That's true.

26:41.680 --> 26:43.070
The incident with Li Lejun

26:43.070 --> 26:45.670
alienated you
from Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

26:45.920 --> 26:47.000
If Her Majesty

26:47.410 --> 26:48.960
really wants to kill you,

26:49.920 --> 26:51.880
she won't stop easily.

26:57.030 --> 26:58.240
You also want

26:58.830 --> 27:02.350
Her Majesty and Xiao Wuyi
to fight each other.

27:03.030 --> 27:05.350
I heard you have a nephew,

27:05.790 --> 27:07.450
whom you treat as your own son.

27:07.790 --> 27:09.440
Back then, you wanted to use the He family

27:09.440 --> 27:11.240
to secure an official career for him.

27:11.240 --> 27:12.100
Unexpectedly,

27:12.240 --> 27:14.270
he was led by the worthless sons
of the He family

27:14.270 --> 27:16.230
to drink and make merry all day,

27:16.270 --> 27:18.270
and almost became a useless person.

27:18.750 --> 27:20.830
His Majesty's chronic illness
is now hard to cure.

27:20.830 --> 27:22.120
How many more years do you think

27:22.120 --> 27:24.450
the Empress Dowager will remain in power?

27:24.960 --> 27:26.000
Why not

27:27.160 --> 27:28.420
form a good tie with me?

27:48.440 --> 27:49.110
Wuyi.

27:51.000 --> 27:52.400
Thank you for your help today.

27:52.400 --> 27:53.940
If you hadn't brought
Imperial Physician Qin,

27:53.940 --> 27:56.160
the Empress Dowager might have succeeded.

27:56.160 --> 27:58.490
Xie Jiayu has already gone after Li Lejun.

28:11.200 --> 28:11.850
Lejun.

28:16.920 --> 28:18.180
Hope you've been well.

28:22.910 --> 28:24.030
I originally thought the Antai Gate

28:24.030 --> 28:25.030
was the Empress Dowager's doing.

28:25.030 --> 28:26.290
It turned out to be you,

28:27.160 --> 28:28.680
constantly using her and me

28:28.680 --> 28:30.280
to create chaos in Jiankang.

28:31.400 --> 28:33.400
As long as the defense battalion's
troops are mobilized

28:33.400 --> 28:34.720
and the Court of Judicial Review's
guard is down,

28:34.720 --> 28:37.240
you could find an opportunity
to swap out Li Lejun

28:37.240 --> 28:38.770
and send her out of the city.

28:39.160 --> 28:40.830
But at least, I helped you
get rid of the Empress Dowager.

28:40.830 --> 28:41.890
Is that not enough?

28:42.640 --> 28:44.350
Right and wrong,
and the bottom line of human life—

28:44.350 --> 28:45.610
I understand them all.

28:46.030 --> 28:48.070
But Li Lejun will always be my exception.

28:48.070 --> 28:50.240
So I left the choice to Xie Jiayu.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.560
Xiao Wuyi, you are too cruel,

28:55.030 --> 28:56.640
to both me and Xie Jiayu.

28:57.200 --> 29:00.240
Do you think she'll be able
to let it go if she kills Lejun?

29:00.240 --> 29:00.830
No.

29:01.750 --> 29:04.080
It will only make it harder
for her to face.

29:04.350 --> 29:06.010
I secretly swapped Lejun out,

29:06.110 --> 29:07.310
then she can survive,

29:07.400 --> 29:09.030
and Xie Jiayu would think
she has gotten her revenge.

29:09.030 --> 29:10.110
Isn't that the best arrangement?

29:10.110 --> 29:11.840
You underestimated Xie Jiayu.

29:12.000 --> 29:13.800
She's not that easily defeated.

29:15.480 --> 29:16.480
She can make a choice.

29:16.480 --> 29:17.550
And this choice

29:18.530 --> 29:19.970
can only be made by her.

29:21.160 --> 29:21.830
Jiayu,

29:22.440 --> 29:25.110
there was no personal grudge
between Princess Yunzhao and me—

29:25.110 --> 29:26.510
only political rivalry.

29:26.510 --> 29:27.710
I had no other choice.

29:27.920 --> 29:29.650
Give me a reason not to kill you.

29:32.030 --> 29:32.590
Fine.

29:33.830 --> 29:34.750
Then today,

29:36.030 --> 29:37.760
I will avenge my mother myself.

29:37.920 --> 29:39.070
If Mao finds out,

29:39.600 --> 29:40.920
he won't let you go.

29:41.960 --> 29:43.690
Then let him come to me himself.

29:44.050 --> 29:45.380
I can go to Northern Qin.

29:46.070 --> 29:47.870
The Eagle King wants to marry me.

29:48.510 --> 29:49.920
I can use this

29:50.640 --> 29:52.570
and go undercover in Northern Qin.

29:52.640 --> 29:55.900
Cui Jun went undercover in Ye
for Northern Qin for 20 years.

29:56.010 --> 29:56.940
If he could do it,

29:58.110 --> 29:58.790
I can too.

30:00.160 --> 30:01.200
Mao is the Regent.

30:01.790 --> 30:03.510
If I go undercover in Northern Qin,

30:03.510 --> 30:05.070
you can trust my loyalty.

30:05.590 --> 30:06.510
I'll be a spy

30:06.830 --> 30:08.920
to help Mao realize his ambitions

30:09.270 --> 30:12.030
and keep Xiao Wuyi informed
of Northern Qin's movements.

30:12.030 --> 30:14.000
Besides, being a spy
is extremely dangerous.

30:14.000 --> 30:16.440
Even if I'm killed
by the Northern Qin people,

30:16.440 --> 30:17.840
it won't be by your hands.

30:19.590 --> 30:20.400
Jiayu.

30:22.830 --> 30:23.960
We are friends.

30:25.200 --> 30:26.000
I don't want

30:27.200 --> 30:28.960
you to kill me with your own hands.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.220
Let's leave it to fate.

30:49.610 --> 30:51.070
Xiao Wuyi, let me tell you,

30:51.440 --> 30:52.240
from now on,

30:52.240 --> 30:54.240
there is no brotherhood between us.

30:59.400 --> 31:01.460
Only a bond of sovereign and subject.

31:50.070 --> 31:50.930
What happened?

31:52.200 --> 31:53.060
Did Mao hit you?

31:54.350 --> 31:54.950
I'm sorry.

31:55.550 --> 31:56.480
Don't overthink it.

31:56.480 --> 31:57.940
This is between him and me.

31:58.640 --> 32:00.300
-It's all my fault.
-Alright.

32:00.350 --> 32:00.920
I'm fine.

32:09.720 --> 32:10.550
Xiao Wuyi.

32:11.720 --> 32:12.830
Although I said

32:13.110 --> 32:14.970
I didn't want to be a demon's wife,

32:15.440 --> 32:16.680
but a hero's wife,

32:17.440 --> 32:20.830
actually, I'm not afraid of

32:21.720 --> 32:23.520
being condemned and notorious.

32:27.350 --> 32:28.550
Why don't you ask me

32:29.000 --> 32:30.460
if I did anything to Lejun?

32:34.240 --> 32:34.970
Are you okay?

32:38.030 --> 32:40.310
She said she wanted
to go to Northern Qin as a spy

32:40.310 --> 32:42.110
and stay undercover
by the Eagle King's side.

32:42.110 --> 32:43.160
I shot an arrow.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.310
Li Lejun.

32:55.720 --> 32:57.120
We shall never meet again

32:57.510 --> 32:58.440
in this life.

32:59.960 --> 33:01.020
If we do meet again,

33:01.750 --> 33:03.610
I will definitely take your life.

33:10.310 --> 33:11.180
Take her to Northern Qin.

33:11.180 --> 33:11.700
Yes.

33:25.750 --> 33:27.750
Princess Yunzhao will understand.

34:02.240 --> 34:06.170
Congratulations, Your Highness,
on taking full control of Jiankang.

34:06.720 --> 34:08.670
Has the Empress Dowager departed yet?

34:08.670 --> 34:10.400
The Empress Dowager
suffered an attack of intense anger,

34:10.400 --> 34:11.630
was invaded by pathogenic wind,

34:11.630 --> 34:12.560
and had a stroke.

34:12.710 --> 34:14.670
She can hardly get up now.

34:15.320 --> 34:16.920
The seal has been taken back.

34:17.190 --> 34:18.510
Early or late,

34:19.190 --> 34:20.449
she still has to leave.

34:20.670 --> 34:23.960
Your Highness,
the Empress Dowager has truly fallen ill.

34:30.630 --> 34:32.489
Then let her rest and recuperate.

34:32.920 --> 34:35.880
About the matter you promised me before...

34:38.920 --> 34:40.120
Your nephew is smart.

34:40.440 --> 34:43.230
I have promoted him
to Commander of the Imperial Guard.

34:43.230 --> 34:44.690
Thank you, Your Highness.

34:45.920 --> 34:47.000
As for you,

34:49.030 --> 34:50.630
stay in the temporary palace

34:51.280 --> 34:53.000
and look after the Empress Dowager.

34:53.000 --> 34:54.710
I... this...

35:12.400 --> 35:13.660
The winner is decided.

35:14.000 --> 35:16.260
Now that you are
the head of the He family,

35:16.550 --> 35:18.550
why come here to show off your power?

35:19.070 --> 35:21.330
I remember when I was young and studying,

35:22.070 --> 35:23.870
Father and Mother always told me

35:24.400 --> 35:26.200
that I had a very beautiful aunt.

35:27.670 --> 35:29.870
She was a noble lady in Jiankang Palace.

35:30.880 --> 35:32.410
She was beautiful, gentle,

35:32.900 --> 35:34.500
and extremely intelligent.

35:34.590 --> 35:36.510
She excelled in the Four Arts.

35:38.440 --> 35:40.320
She was especially good at
playing the ruanxian.

35:40.320 --> 35:43.800
A piece of "Partridge" would make people
forget all worldly worries.

35:43.800 --> 35:44.670
Father and Mother

35:44.670 --> 35:46.710
pointed at her portrait and told me

35:47.550 --> 35:49.000
that a noble daughter
of an aristocratic family

35:49.000 --> 35:50.200
with elegant bearing

35:50.230 --> 35:51.360
should be like this.

35:52.880 --> 35:55.340
So I imitated her appearance
in the painting

35:56.800 --> 35:57.590
to read,

35:58.880 --> 36:00.210
practice calligraphy,

36:00.880 --> 36:01.740
play the guqin,

36:03.000 --> 36:03.840
and grow up,

36:05.440 --> 36:07.300
wanting to become the second her.

36:10.000 --> 36:10.840
Now,

36:15.630 --> 36:16.960
can you still play?

36:26.630 --> 36:28.280
Later, I met that aunt.

36:28.920 --> 36:30.920
I even brought my ruanxian that day.

36:32.000 --> 36:34.460
But the first thing
she told me when she saw me

36:34.800 --> 36:37.150
was that I needed
to marry a man I had never met

36:37.150 --> 36:39.230
for the sake of the family.

36:41.110 --> 36:42.190
Which noble lady

36:42.920 --> 36:44.150
doesn't marry a man

36:44.150 --> 36:45.480
she has never met?

36:47.070 --> 36:49.240
But I had already agreed,

36:50.710 --> 36:52.950
and Pei Runheng was already dead!

36:53.710 --> 36:55.760
Why did you have to frame them

36:56.230 --> 36:58.160
and destroy the entire Pei family?

36:58.360 --> 36:59.400
Why?

37:02.190 --> 37:03.190
It became a habit.

37:06.990 --> 37:09.880
The Pei family refused to believe
their son died in an accident.

37:09.880 --> 37:11.920
How could I let them keep digging

37:12.630 --> 37:14.090
and causing more trouble?

37:30.230 --> 37:32.710
When Runheng's mother committed suicide
with her daughter,

37:32.710 --> 37:35.110
his younger sister
was not even 5 years old!

37:36.540 --> 37:37.310
Aunt.

37:38.360 --> 37:40.290
Because of your own lust for power,

37:40.400 --> 37:42.480
how many lives have you ruined?

37:43.230 --> 37:44.090
Lust for power?

37:44.360 --> 37:46.160
Who is born with a lust for power?

37:46.210 --> 37:48.290
The He family ruined my life as well.

37:48.360 --> 37:49.690
Who will cry foul for me?

37:50.070 --> 37:51.030
Without me,

37:51.150 --> 37:52.230
the He family would be nothing

37:52.230 --> 37:53.760
but an insignificant clan.

37:53.840 --> 37:55.710
All the wealth and glory you enjoy now

37:55.710 --> 37:57.440
were bought with my sacrifice.

37:57.880 --> 38:00.400
What? Now that you're done using me,

38:01.550 --> 38:03.350
you want to wash your hands of it?

38:05.840 --> 38:08.510
But your luck is better than mine
after all.

38:09.150 --> 38:10.610
Prince Jing'an's Mansion

38:11.280 --> 38:13.480
is not the man-eating Jiankang Palace.

38:29.440 --> 38:31.030
It's all an illusion.

38:32.430 --> 38:34.030
Old friends are not the same.

38:35.480 --> 38:37.080
You probably don't know yet.

38:38.400 --> 38:39.190
His Majesty

38:40.480 --> 38:42.410
has already issued a secret edict.

38:43.960 --> 38:45.550
The day he passes away

38:47.960 --> 38:50.670
will be the day you die.

38:52.070 --> 38:53.530
The future of the He family

38:56.170 --> 38:58.770
has absolutely nothing
to do with you anymore.

39:12.940 --> 39:15.260
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

39:18.840 --> 39:22.170
Cui Jun died without entering
the Court of Judicial Review.

39:22.230 --> 39:24.360
Whether he was truly a Northern Qin spy

39:24.510 --> 39:28.110
or he fabricated the unjust case
involving the An and Lu families

39:29.050 --> 39:30.510
can no longer be verified.

39:33.000 --> 39:35.000
What about the Phoenix Heart Token?

39:35.510 --> 39:36.770
It is with His Majesty.

39:59.880 --> 40:01.230
Crown Prince Wenxi.

40:02.480 --> 40:04.880
It has been returned
to its rightful owner.

40:06.280 --> 40:08.110
Are you sure Xiao Wuyi

40:08.480 --> 40:09.740
is Crown Prince Wenxi?

40:10.000 --> 40:11.630
He definitely is.

40:15.400 --> 40:16.150
I...

40:17.190 --> 40:18.590
I didn't know you knew...

40:19.150 --> 40:20.550
Let it be.

40:21.670 --> 40:24.590
It is a blessing not to know.

40:27.960 --> 40:29.890
I don't have many days left to live.

40:32.190 --> 40:33.720
And I no longer have the will

40:34.920 --> 40:37.230
to save the people of this world.

40:37.920 --> 40:40.380
I don't want to deal with
this massive flood,

40:40.920 --> 40:42.550
and I can't anyway.

40:43.000 --> 40:45.840
Are you just going to leave it be?

40:48.440 --> 40:50.630
Crown Prince Wenxi's Phoenix Heart Token

40:50.630 --> 40:52.320
originally belonged to him.

40:54.670 --> 40:56.360
I will use my own way

40:56.800 --> 40:57.510
to beat him.
